Package: shinybrain
Title: Illustrate the evolution of a Shiny application from prototype to finished product
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Eric", "Nantz","theRcast@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of shinybrain is to provide a simple procedure to create multiple snapshots of an overall Shiny application. The ability to show the development journey inside a single overall application is a great benefit to educating others on the iterative nature of Shiny application development.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
